AUDIO: 'of course, you first need to generate a video, or maybe you have an existing video. But, in this case, just to break down this whole scene, I first generated an image using Crea 2. It\'s the image generator that I\'m enjoying using at the moment. Once I\'ve got my image, I can'

[01:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'then turn it into a video using Seidons 2.0. Now, to gain access to Seedons 2.0, lucky for you, it\'s available on a multitude of different websites from Dreamina, CapCut, Runway, HiLo, OpenArt. It really depends what platform you want'

[02:07] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'to use. The two that I would recommend is dreamina.capcut.com. You can see I\'ve got access to Seedons 2.0 and the Omni reference. This is very important. This allows you to upload various types of references from images, audio, and even videos. And that\'s'

