AUDIO: 'rid of that and make it seamless. So, the solution for this is actually shockingly simple, but it does require some finesse and also some good judgment. Basically, what you want to do is with your extended clip, you want to'

[09:55] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'drag it and you basically want to overlap it on your previous clips. I\'ll just drag this back a little bit and what we basically going to be doing over here is we want to eliminate that additional frame. So, the easiest way'

