[10:33] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'and drag my clip over here until it lines up perfectly. Now, from my experimenting, I actually had to go back five frames with my clip and remember that\'s not a definitive value, that\'s why you need to experiment. So, I\'m'

