VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'going to go 1 2 3 4 5 and if I drag my clip over here, you\'ll see that using this opacity, I can see exactly where that clip lines up, which means that from this point on, this is going to be a perfect and seamless extension. So,'

[10:58] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
